{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, he had so much tattooing of chest and back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was not a square inch left vacant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was incarcerated in 1933 as a communist in Dachau when Hitler put up the first camp in Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And before that, he was in Foreign Legion in, in Africa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was the boss.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Lagerschreiber, which was a very nice man, he was originally from the Yugoslav foreign ministry, an, an, an officer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was going with the two Germans who counted us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he write how many people, how--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--many sick, and so on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he arranged that that, that hot day, we could swim.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the Appell, they told us, you can leave your clothing on the spot where you stand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And naked, we can walk out, march out outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only a hundred meters past the guards' barracks, were a big excavation of sand for a-- for a building company.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was called Moll, M-O double L.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [GERMAN] and [GERMAN], the two of them, they both were excavating sand for big construction in BMW.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some of these were filled with water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was quite deep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some were 3, 4 meters deep, and straight deep, not gradually.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were allowed to swim, a whole lot of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whoever was not sick, who wanted to go for a swim went for a swim.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Over about 500, 600 people went for a swim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- there was, like, five swimming pools put together, square.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were big cranes which took the stuff out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When it was full of water, they dig another one next to it, send the excavation only for concreting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came back-- it was splashing, so many people there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
